Download Node js

URL: https://nodejs.org/en/download/

After installing node js the below command:
node -v
npm -v

Download Angular:

url: https://angular.io/cli

execute the below command to install angular
npm install -g @angular/cli


Install Babel:
npm install @babel/core @babel/preset-env @babel/node

create the file .babelrc


Angualar:
If you get any security issue error
Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser


--create new project
ng new project-one

cd project-one

--start the project
ng serve

